{"tid":1838903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港是中國的龍脈，龍脈有損，天降瘟疫","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T07:55:04.000Z","uid":266959,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7683e1b7039cdc8fa00bb5a80a3488d331ecb9a5","tid":1838903,"uid":266959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:48:05.000Z","msg":"百多年前，新思潮經香港入神州引發大革命，而有中國，香港因此是龍興之地，一國命脈所在。文革浩劫之後，資本由香港入中國而能延續一黨專政統治，香港因此是中興之地，國運所系。香港好則中國好，損害香港乃自掘墳墓，自斷龍脈，而今天再降警告，支那小民還不快恭聽天意！"},{"pid":"6f834bf646c6c22cc92b0f3ff493bc2e518d26b9","tid":1838903,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"}]}